# Tidecast runs with ZERO required environment variables.
# Every on-chain constant (the DeepBook Predict package, the Predict server URL,
# the dUSDC type, the network) is hardcoded for testnet in src/lib/constants.ts.
#
# You only need a .env.local if you want to override a default below.
# Copy this file to .env.local and uncomment what you need.

# Optional — pre-seed the in-app wallet on first run with an existing testnet key.
# If unset, the app shows onboarding and you click "Generate a new wallet" in the UI.
# VITE_TIDECAST_KEYPAIR=suiprivkey1...

# Optional — network override (default: testnet). Tidecast is testnet-only today.
# VITE_SUI_NETWORK=testnet
